    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mas, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You fire a ray of flames at your target, dealing 1d6 fire damage. If you hold a weapon with a Homura Dama effect active on it, you can instead discharge the effect to deal damage equal to the Homura Dama's. The effect is discharged even if the attack misses.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step increases the range to Long.</p>\n",
